window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Events have shown Meghan that protecting her kids also means making sure they're ready to stand on their own when needed.</b></p> <p>That's always been part of her parenting philosophy, but applying it to letting a six-year-old get up close and personal with vicious monsters? Questionable! Certainly not easy.</p> <p>Meghan needs to figure out a way, however, and the aliens won't let her sit down and figure it out. While wrestling these personal dilemmas, she also needs to keep stabilizing her area, find a way to deal with these mysterious new Titans, and deal with some other nasty twists humanity's alien tormentors have in store.</p>"; 
